// Zanna.IO.Path - static utility class for path manipulation
/// @summary Provides static utility class for path manipulation.
/// @details
/// `Zanna.IO.Path` exposes a registry-backed runtime surface without requiring callers to construct
/// the class directly. Its public surface exposes operations including `Absolute`, `Directory`,
/// `Extension`, `ExeDir`.
